title: Elvira, or The Worst Not Always True

items: Don Fernando Solis: In love with Donna Elvira.
Don Zancho de Menezes: In love with Donna Blanca.
Donna Elvira: A beautiful Lady, Don Pedro's Daughter.
Donna Blanca: A Lady of a high Spirit Don Julio's Sister.
Silvia: Elvira's disguised Name, when she was put to wait upon Donna Blanca.

speeches.speaker: D. Jul. [ to Silvia as he leads her . ]
Donna Blanca [ as he is going . ]
Fernando [ as he follows him Aside . ]
Silv. [ Putting her Handkercher to her Eyes . ]
Don Zancho [ holding out his Sword . ]
Fer. striving to come at Zancho . ]
